{"tid":316935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞人=金，支那人=蒙古！！","createTime":"2017-07-11T05:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T08:20:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ccda91a2d2f8649311426a5ed23243f4d5dadb2","tid":316935,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:59:11.000Z","msg":"我認為應該「扶金抗蒙」，我認為蒙古現在已經強大到足以滅金，如果放任金國被滅，那麼蒙古兵鋒很快就會對準南宋，與其如此，我們不如繼續給金國歲幣，這樣讓金國能夠繼續抗蒙，南宋則可以爭取更多的時間積極備戰，應對蒙古將來的入侵。<br />\n這種想法可以說是很有戰略遠見，當時金宋之間互相之間雖然都看不過眼，但都對對方無可奈何，然而蒙古不同，他是有能力將宋金一鍋端的傢伙，這時候宋金聯合方是上策，南宋在經濟上支持金國，讓金國去消耗，這樣既削弱蒙古，也給自己爭取時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/vp5pgl.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhistory%2Fvp5pgl.html&d=RWfcpYAj8BCAA7VXPsDiDLZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=4f66abf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/history/vp5pgl.html</a>"},{"pid":"acf12c2b66760ff70fc54987748fa505bf1071e0","tid":316935,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:18:10.000Z","msg":"香港人=黑奴"},{"pid":"55fffbf04fe2f169f2400280949e917695e8c041","tid":316935,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"但歷史係聯蒙滅金"},{"pid":"a85fb570c47b8f50974a870755db5ef100f50cf0","tid":316935,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:21:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但歷史係聯蒙滅金</blockquote><br />\n所以更應以史為鑒"},{"pid":"25447094664e520a9999c7c2b01169c48f88f901","tid":316935,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:34:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e71c0fa5fb31c2369fad876887495ef7754cfa74","tid":316935,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T06:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻西<br />\n金人有奶就是娘<br />\n你憑咩扶</blockquote><br />\n切記「唇齒相依，唇亡齒寒」，「兩害之間權其輕」的策略"},{"pid":"ddaab7d317dedbdfbf5d376619a0ded3954c99a3","tid":316935,"uid":44646,"like":0,"disl